{"tid":1648814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱係長沙灣道運動場十字路口巴/絲打玩家入","createTime":"2019-10-12T11:21:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T11:47:24.000Z","uid":146464,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5ce9c5919207c838d44b2eaf4b9f839c816accc2","tid":1648814,"uid":146464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:21:35.000Z","msg":"啱啱大型online攻略就到尾聲<br />\n我就見到有一班玩家係度爭論<br />\n由於後面玩家被 Boss Cut斷<br />\n所以有絲打想番去一齊打Boss<br />\n就比一個企咗上欄杆嘅巴打屌<br />\n巴打就想快閃send RB之後閃水<br />\n絲打就想番去救玩家<br />\n但大家都唔知後面有幾多Boss<br />\n所以就互屌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講咗咁多<br />\n我想講四個月大型online<br />\n支持住大家嘅係信任<br />\n我知大家有時好關心玩家安全<br />\n有咩事平心靜氣傾<br />\n一人退一步 求一個最好嘅辨法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好唔好？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw欄杆巴打玩家頭髮染咗特別顏色下次戴番頂帽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係好易認<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又要企得高而且有記者影住<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3c51519ad5e0e5a44a892288f6dce9740538f18","tid":1648814,"uid":70973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:32:06.000Z","msg":"一句野解釋晒點解場運動會輸<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648803\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648803</a>"},{"pid":"d2d2ea78dadc31735eedc74d7de820d98ff88b3b","tid":1648814,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:33:10.000Z","msg":"<strong>支持住大家嘅係信任</strong><br />\n<br />\n緊記"},{"pid":"e4df43674554c5884fa3d7d27f9dd4336b02c93c","tid":1648814,"uid":172465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:38:43.000Z","msg":"信任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d403a57b05f1f0ca2037bca7fb1d07b7dec485d0","tid":1648814,"uid":22692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:43:27.000Z","msg":"佢地屌但都好平心靜氣"},{"pid":"c4b373434e5aeeea92d4353985ef9c05e6f19bce","tid":1